_json.gridTitle: “To argue that God is “trying His best” to save all mankind, but that the majority of men will not let Him save them, is to insist that the will of the Creator is impotent, and that the will of the creature is omnipotent.”    ― Arthur W. Pink, The Sovereignty of God
